data.description: Waterfront cedar sided home with covered boat house, stationery pier, floating dock, covered patio, open deck, circular drive, detached storage building/workshop, attached storage area, 2-car carport with pull down attic access and a very gentle slope to the water for easy enjoyment.  The top level features a loft master bedroom w/vaulted ceiling, single closet, walk-in closet and bath w/garden tub.  The main level hosts an open floor plan w/living room w/stone fireplace, breakfast area, kitchen w/breakfast bar, stove, dishwasher & refrigerator, large dining room, 2 spare bedrooms and a full bath.  The basement has a wonderful den w/wet bar, full bath, bonus room that could be the 4th bedroom & a large laundry room.
